These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, corn, pineapple, apricot
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, august, october, january
1. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating cherry##5
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
3. the person who's birthday is in september is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
5. the person who's birthday is in september is the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating pineapple is the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Food      | apricot  | cherry | corn  | pineapple |
| Birthday   | october | january      | september | august |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, fonseca, bolivar, prince
There 4 different types of food: carrot, strawberry, watermelon, pumpkin
1. the fonseca-smoker is between the person eating carrot and the person eating pumpkin##2
2. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5
3. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating carrot is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Cigar   | prince | bolivar | fonseca   | ritmeester |
| Food           | watermelon      | carrot    | strawberry | pumpkin      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, aquamarine, mauve
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, engineer, architect, social-worker
1. the person who likes coral is the engineer##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
3. the architect is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
4. the dancer is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
5. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
6. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the left of the architect##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Color        | coral | turquise | aquamarine     | mauve |
| Job   | engineer  | social-worker   | architect | dancer    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, dancer, scientist, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the pilot is on the left of the dancer##1
2. the coach is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
3. the pilot is between the person driving the taxi and the person driving the scooter##2
4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the taxi is the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Job         | scientist | pilot | dancer | coach |
| Transport   | taxi   | subway     | scooter    | motorbike       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, october, august
4 different pets are kept: snake, bird, dog, turtle
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the owner of the snake##5
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Birthday          | october | august   | september   | november    |
| Pet   | bird  | turtle | snake | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, musical, western
City: london, edinburgh, paris, marseilles
1. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching spy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
3. the person traveling to marseilles is between the person watching western movies and the person traveling to paris##2
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Movie-Genre           | spy | zombie | western | musical |
| City   | paris        | marseilles     | london       | edinburgh   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-7::.
City: boston, marseilles, liverpool, london
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, swimming, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person traveling to london##1
2. the person traveling to boston is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person who's sport is rowing##2
3. the person who's sport is cycling is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5
5. the person traveling to boston is in an even position##4
6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| City   | marseilles | boston  | liverpool  | london   |
| Sport           | weightlifting  | cycling | rowing | swimming |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
City: berlin, liverpool, paris, nizza
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, techno, gospel, salsa
1. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the person traveling to nizza is somewhere to the left of the fan of gospel##5
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the fan of metal##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| City   | liverpool     | nizza | paris     | berlin   |
| Music-Genre    | salsa | techno  | gospel | metal |

