.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  police-officer, electrician, scientist, pilot
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, camping, collecting, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the police-officer##1
2. the scientist is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the police-officer is on the left of the scientist##1
4. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
5. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##5
6. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Job   | police-officer | scientist | pilot   | electrician |
| Hobby       | photography       | collecting   | puzzles | camping |

