.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, amaryllis, daffodil
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, prince, swisher, dannemann
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
2. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaffodil##5
3. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
4. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere to the right of the dannemann-smoker##5
5. the prince-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsorchid##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Flower   | poppy | amaryllis       | orchid   | daffodil        |
| Cigar      | prince  | dannemann | aristoff | swisher |

