.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, spinach, orange, onion
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, cola, juice
1. the person eating blueberry is somewhere to the left of the person eating spinach##5
2. the person drinking cola is the person eating orange##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
7. the person eating orange is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Food   | blueberry | spinach   | orange | onion     |
| Beverage   | coffee     | soy-milk | cola  | juice |

