.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, kale, cucumber, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: american, spanish, mexican, thai
1. the thai is on the left of the american##1
2. the thai is in an even position##4
3. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
4. the person eating apricot is the mexican##1
5. the person eating avocado is somewhere to the right of the person eating cucumber##5
6. the spanish is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Food   | apricot | cucumber        | avocado        | kale |
| Nationality         | mexican  | thai | american | spanish |

