.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, epic, fantasy, superhero
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, weightlifting, surfing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an odd position##4
4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy | superhero | epic | animation |
| Sport   | soccer     | cricket  | weightlifting  | surfing    |

