.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, mauve, ebony, purple
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, skydiving, filmmaking, board-games
1. the person who likes green is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
2. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is chess##5
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person who likes mauve is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Color   | purple  | green | mauve | ebony |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | chess | skydiving   | board-games  |

