.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different games are played: canasta, mah-jongg, poker, domino
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, blue, grey, yellow
1. the person playing domino is between the person playing poker and the person playing mah-jongg##2
2. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person playing domino##3
3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
5. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
6. the person who likes grey is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Game   | canasta | poker  | domino      | mah-jongg |
| Color     | grey    | yellow | blue | apricot   |

