.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, march, january, june
The people have 4 different jobs:  journalist, scientist, project-manager, fisherman
1. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the journalist is in an even position##4
5. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
6. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person who's birthday is in february and the scientist##2
7. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday      | february   | january  | march      | june       |
| Job   | project-manager | fisherman | scientist | journalist |

