.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-17::.
4 different pets are kept: turtle, hamster, pony, bird
House: futuristic, victorian, craftsman, colonial
1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
2. the owner of the pony is the colonial house##1
3. the futuristic house is on the right of the victorian house##1
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
5. the craftsman house is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Pet   | turtle     | hamster | bird | pony |
| House     | victorian | futuristic    | craftsman    | colonial |

