.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-18::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, doctor, paramedic, chef
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, crime, satire, horror
1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching horror movies##5
3. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the left of the dancer##5
4. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the doctor##5
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the dancer is between the chef and the person watching crime movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3     |       4       |
| Job      | paramedic     | chef | dancer     | doctor |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | sports | crime        |

