.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, may, august, april
4 different games are played: whist, poker, backgammon, go
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person playing poker and the person who's birthday is in may##2
2. the person playing whist is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
3. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person playing go##5
4. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday         | august   | april   | february       | may   |
| Game   | backgammon | poker | whist | go |

