.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
House: modern, wooden, victorian, cottage
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, poppy, begonia, tulip
1. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person who growspoppy##5
2. the modern house is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
3. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
5. the wooden house is somewhere to the left of the person who growstulip##5
6. the modern house is between the cottage house and the person who growsamaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| House        | wooden     | cottage | modern | victorian |
| Flower   | begonia | tulip | poppy      | amaryllis        |

 